I'm now focused on enabling the "Add Teacher" button, and have plans to open a modal upon click. I'll integrate this in `TeacherList.tsx` by adding an `onAdd` prop and a state management system with a modal to add teacher records. I'm now adding a password input into the state of the modal in `TeacherList.tsx`. The password field is already in `types.ts`, so I am ready to implement the Teacher form to match the updated student form.

