                    <ol className="list-decimal ml-5 space-y-1">
                        <li>Go to Firebase Console &gt; Project Settings &gt; General</li>
                        <li>Scroll to "Your apps" and select the Web app</li>
                        <li>Copy the <code>firebaseConfig</code> object (JSON)</li>
                        <li>Paste it below and click Connect</li>
                    </ol>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <label className="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Firebase Config JSON</label>
                    <textarea 
                        rows={6}
